title: Dickies Shop Shirt LL605
description: Dickies Performance Shop Shirt - Need a work shirt that can hold up to any tough job and still look great?  Introducing Dickies Performance Shop Shirt.  This stylish shirt offers contrast color block detail on the shoulder for an updated fashionable look.  It is loaded with performance features like moisture wicking, stain release, resists wrinkles and is made with 4.6-oz flex twill fabric for ease of movement.  And its industrial laundry friendly.  Available in both short and long sleeves, this shirt is the perfect shirt for any uniform program.  Dickies, The Name the Pros Know and Trust.
